name: dannet
description: DanNet ====== [DanNet](https://cst.ku.dk/projekter/dannet/) is a [WordNet](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WordNet) for the Danish language. The goal of this project is to represent DanNet in full using [RDF](https://www.w3.org/RDF/) as its native representation at both the database level, in the application space, and as its primary serialisation format.
